                  <additions>
                     <lb/>
                     <label>Inscriptions:</label> The <locus from="iva" to="iva">right flyleaf a
                        side (f. iva)</locus> bears the title of the work and author, describes its
                     subject, and notes the date of completion.<lb/> Folio <locus from="1a" to="1a"
